报告等证明材料。 案发后，当事人分别于2018年3月、2018年4月13日改正了倩碧鲜活维C修复精华液、ORIGINS榆绿木青春紧弹塑颜霜的网页宣传内容。 上海市静安区市监局认定雅诗兰黛旗下的“倩碧”和“悦木之源”在天猫旗舰店的产品页面所作的商品宣传，存在违反《反不正当竞争法》第8条第1款“经营者不得对其商品的性能、功能、质量、销售状况、用户评价、曾获荣誉等作虚假或者引人误解的商业宣传，欺骗、误导消费者”规定，对其处以罚款40万元。雅诗兰黛因虚假宣传被罚40万 - 经济观察网 － 专业财经新闻网站"},"attached_info":"Cj8IxofTnomUx4IgEAMaCDY2NDEwNTg3ILWR54YGMAU4nAJAEXIJNDY4NTg4NjkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"204 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc46a8f74c404c05c7cd3cbe419a68c9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1624964744.4182768","card_id":"Q_468180174","target":{"id":468180174,"title":"《海贼王》1017话是否代表海贼王走上火影的老路？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/468180174","type":"question","created":1624780173,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":181,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[163041,396543],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如果橡胶果实暗藏玄机，还有路飞和乔伊波伊的关系，后面一旦被实锤了，就和火影中的转世论如出一辙。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IxofTnomUx4IgEAMaCDY2MzE5NjcwII3b4IYGMAM4tQFAEnIJNDY4MTgwMTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"199 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d85057f579547a97e54f50f684554659_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1624964744.4188905","card_id":"Q_468659107","target":{"id":468659107,"title":"如何评价 Windows 11 首个预览版 Build 22000.51 ？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/468659107","type":"question","created":1624904186,"answer_count":23,"follower_count":62,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[797,44997,105508,725059,725185],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"今天（6月29日）凌晨，Build 22000.51开始向Dev通道推送。"},"attached_i